panels.content:
<center>Select reporter of your choice from drop down menu to analyze propagation to his location / antenna.</center>
<center>Select reporter2 for comparison to reporter 1 - selectors could select more than 1; bandl selects the observed bands.</center> 
<center>Select beacon call sign for comparison on all bands; you can deselect all, type the first characters to reduce the list. click to end selction</center>
panels.title: DK5HH & PA7T WSPRlive analysis

targets.query: SELECT count("snr") FROM "wspr_main" WHERE "reporter" =~ /^$rprtr$/  AND "dist" > $localstn AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "band"

panels.title: Sum of all bands / hour (based on 10 min)

targets.query: SELECT moving_average(count("snr"),3)  * 6 FROM "wspr_main" WHERE "reporter" =~ /^$rprtr$/ AND "dist" > $localstn AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10m), "band"

panels.title: All bands - moving average (w=3) based on 10 min - scaled to  spots per hour

targets.query: SELECT distinct("snr") FROM "wspr_main" WHERE "call" =~ /^P[A-I].*$/ AND "reporter" =~ /^$rprtr$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "band" ,"call" fill(null)
SELECT distinct("snr") FROM "wspr_main" WHERE "call" =~ /^$beacon$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(2m), "band", "reporter"
SELECT mean("dist") FROM "wspr_main" WHERE "band" =~ /[12]/ AND "loc" =~ /^[JIK][MNOP].*/ and "dist" >100 AND "dist" < 2000 AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20m), "band" fill(none)

panels.title: short-skips in EU: mean(Distance) - locators J,I,K, (by 20min)

targets.query: SELECT count("dist") FROM "wspr_main" WHERE "band" =~ /[12]/ AND "loc" =~ /^[JIK][MNOP].*/ AND "dist" > 100 AND "dist" < 2000 AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20m), "band" fill(none)
